<h1>My Personal Recommendation</h1>
Buy the KSCi5. I own the UR40s, Porta Pros, and the KSC75s. The KSC75s have the best sound by far. The crazy part is that they're only $26.00 dollars (CAD), which is half of the price of the UR40s, and a third of the price of Porta Pros. Once you try them, you won't think about buying any other headphones than these ones.

